In a shallow bowl, combine cumin, cinnamon, coriander, red pepper, salt. Dredge chicken in spices. In a large skillet, heat oil over medium heat. Add chicken; saute until browned, turning once. Remove chicken. Add onion; saute 3 minutes. Add garlic, ginger, broth; saute 5 minutes. Add tomatoes, chick peas, olives, raisins, honey, bay leaf, cinnamon, lemon and chicken. Cover; simmer 30 minutes. Serve in bowls, with toasted whole wheat pitas.